{"tid":1054544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"研究證廣東話小朋友先天音感勁過普通話人","createTime":"2019-03-10T01:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T06:19:34.000Z","uid":171273,"like":108,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9fec3504f4576199b779d6813e9c53483da30179","tid":1054544,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"19年03月09號<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/1941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F1941&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2IE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=50c97959\" target=\"_blank\">http://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/1941</a><br />\n<br />\nCNN曾將「先天音感」(Tonal talent)譽為香港十大無敵優點之首，原來早有研究發現，用廣東話嘅小朋友音感比普通話嘅更強：「Cantonese-speaking children had more advanced tone awareness than Mandarin-speaking children. This was likely because Cantonese has a more complicated tone system than Mandarin.」<br />\n小學禁絕本港學童講其母語廣東話有違《兒童權利公約》，亟待主持公道。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員做咗兩次試驗，用普通話、與廣東話共通字、假字（Pseudo words）辨音做測試。佢地發現，廣東話小朋友無論喺辨認聲調(Tone)、頭子音(Onset)、韻攝(Rime)，能力都凌駕普通話小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/canpthchart.png?w=720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fcanpthchart.png%3Fw%3D720&h=afd7439c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到廣東話小朋友每樣分數都高過人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/12301487_993431264046932_5363920178749422464_n.png?w=728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F12301487_993431264046932_5363920178749422464_n.png%3Fw%3D728&h=d0c3485f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n研究人員考慮到呢個Experiment 1係用普通話字做測試，就做咗Experiment 2，用粵普共通字同假字做，都係發現廣東話小朋友得分高啲。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員將結論歸究兩個原因：廣東話小朋友有雙語環境( bilingualism)以及廣東話有更複雜嘅語音系統。<br />\n<br />\n參考: Chen, X., Anderson, R., Li, W., Hao, M., Wu, X., &amp; Shu, H. (2004). Phonological Awareness of Bilingual and Monolingual Chinese Children. Journal of Educational Psychology, 96(1), 142-151."},{"pid":"9151cf20820f3b7083594d7994a99741866dad18","tid":1054544,"uid":83063,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌   而家香港啲小朋友邊只 bilingual"},{"pid":"0dcfb1a4e588686fd53fe051f9500455149cd4c9","tid":1054544,"uid":23170,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"其實已經唔關邊種語言可以幫到小朋友多啲，之前嗰啲乜柒有助書寫能力都俾人批過，明眼人都知根本就係要溝淡香港文化。唯有反共先可以keep住香港本土文化"},{"pid":"1b1b38b80bec41f7cee0fd7605faa29533fcb768","tid":1054544,"uid":171273,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"0dcfb1a4e588686fd53fe051f9500455149cd4c9","tid":1054544,"uid":23170,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"其實已經唔關邊種語言可以幫到小朋友多啲，之前嗰啲乜柒有助書寫能力都俾人批過，明眼人都知根本就係要溝淡香港文化。唯有反共先可以keep住香港本土文化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"有D老豆老母真係以為學蝗語會叻D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73345677ee4d40b32e54ec303d4a14790eb1027","tid":1054544,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T01:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c064cc70b78c9695c2caeb7e17ee5600c0fc314e","tid":1054544,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"其實好合理 廣東話tone多自然多啲tonal exposure <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987e3742ab0f92dd295f31a7352f2b7dfda3dfd2","tid":1054544,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTi